      "id": "PopularPost34336",
      "post_content": "Very expensive, but once it starts going it's very good. It really shines in multiplayer where you can just have it sit around, killing creatures that would have died anyway (to prevent people getting mad), collecting counters, then getting more mana than you know what to do with.  \n  \nAlso, another card boosted by removing mana burn.",
