      "id": "PopularPost232131",
      "post_content": "\"My question: If you can afford to cast a seven mana artifact why would you need more mana?\"  \n  \nClearly you are not a Timmy. You ALWAYS need more mana. Especially if you want to run this every turn. And if you have this thing in a [prototype portal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=prototype portal), you require the killing to activate more than one per turn. ",
      "posted_by": "kiseki",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost232131\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">\"My question: If you can afford to cast a seven mana artifact why would you need more mana?\"<br/><br/>Clearly you are not a Timmy.  You ALWAYS need more mana.  Especially if you want to run this every turn.  And if you have this thing in a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"prototype portal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=prototype portal\">prototype portal</a>, you require the killing to activate more than one per turn.  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '232131'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy51522\">kiseki</span>\r\n                                (3/8/2012 5:51:29 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/