    {
      "id": "PopularPost18720",
      "post_content": "When compaired to the best Altars printed, [Ashnod's Altar](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ashnod's Altar ) and [Phyrexian Altar](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phyrexian Altar ) , this Altars seems to fall short. However when combined with an [Energy Chamber](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Energy Chamber) and [Power Conduit](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Power Conduit) this card becomes an instant creature destruction engine with the ability to fuel an artifact creature deck or any colorless based deck. The mana requirements needed for this makes this a marginal card at best, however. 3/5",
